title: MASH Bamboo Reusable Cuticle Pushers Remover / Manicure Pedicure Stick
description: MASH is proud to introduce its 10 piece set of cuticle sticks. These sticks have been sourced by the nail art experts at MASH and are made of the finest bamboo from our most trusted suppliers. Manicure and pedicures sticks are sturdy with beveled end for pushing back cuticles and for cleaning under and around the nail. Gently push back cuticles and clean under and around nail beds for an at home manicure anytime!Directions:Hold the file at a slight angle just under your nail. Start with the rough surface and work from one side of the nail toward the center. File in one direction only to prevent splitting. When the nail is shaped as you like, use the fine surface of the file for a smooth, satiny finish that prevents snagging and broken nails.
